Replace the current boost allocation for LAWETP/EMBER with lawUSD/EMBER.

&nbsp; 

 Impact on users

The boost will move automatically to lawUSD/EMBER meaning we will see liquidity on lawUSD/EMBER again.

&nbsp; 

Expected impact

Less liquidity on LAWETP, more liquidity on lawUSD.

&nbsp; 

Expected positive impact

More fees generated as lawUSD has a higher trading volume than LAWETP
